{
  "video_id": "nLB8A--QdHc",
  "title": "3 thoughtful ways to conserve water | Lana Mazahreh",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13573.0,
      "end_time": 15953.0,
      "text": "In March 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15977.0,
      "end_time": 20411.0,
      "text": "the mayor of Cape Town officially declared Cape Town a local disaster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20435.0,
      "end_time": 23226.0,
      "text": "as it had less than four months left of usable water."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24200.0,
      "end_time": 28161.0,
      "text": "Residents were restricted to 100 liters of water per person, per day."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29324.0,
      "end_time": 30846.0,
      "text": "But what does that really mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31721.0,
      "end_time": 33613.0,
      "text": "With 100 liters of water per day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33637.0,
      "end_time": 35401.0,
      "text": "you can take a five-minute shower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36660.0,
      "end_time": 37476.0,
      "text": "wash your face twice"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38170.0,
      "end_time": 40922.0,
      "text": "and probably flush the toilet about five times."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41902.0,
      "end_time": 43546.0,
      "text": "You still didn&#39;t brush your teeth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44835.0,
      "end_time": 46710.0,
      "text": "you didn&#39;t do laundry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46734.0,
      "end_time": 49709.0,
      "text": "and you definitely didn&#39;t water your plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50412.0,
      "end_time": 54380.0,
      "text": "You, unfortunately, didn&#39;t wash your hands after those five toilet flushes."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55910.0,
      "end_time": 57864.0,
      "text": "And you didn&#39;t even take a sip of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60511.0,
      "end_time": 63599.0,
      "text": "The mayor described this as that it means"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63623.0,
      "end_time": 65521.0,
      "text": "a new relationship with water."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67442.0,
      "end_time": 68964.0,
      "text": "Today, seven months later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68988.0,
      "end_time": 71801.0,
      "text": "I can share two things about my second home with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71825.0,
      "end_time": 75270.0,
      "text": "First: Cape Town hasn&#39;t run out of water just yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75378.0,
      "end_time": 77151.0,
      "text": "But as of September 3rd,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77175.0,
      "end_time": 80548.0,
      "text": "the hundred-liter limit dropped to 87 liters."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81300.0,
      "end_time": 85767.0,
      "text": "The mayor defined the city&#39;s new normal as one of permanent drought."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86869.0,
      "end_time": 88324.0,
      "text": "Second:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88348.0,
      "end_time": 91858.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s happening in Cape Town is pretty much coming to many other cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91882.0,
      "end_time": 93238.0,
      "text": "and countries in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93935.0,
      "end_time": 97537.0,
      "text": "According to the Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97561.0,
      "end_time": 99912.0,
      "text": "excluding countries that we don&#39;t have data for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100525.0,
      "end_time": 103688.0,
      "text": "less than five percent of the world&#39;s population"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103712.0,
      "end_time": 108327.0,
      "text": "is living in a country that has more water today than it did 20 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 109309.0,
      "end_time": 112878.0,
      "text": "Everyone else is living in a country that has less water today."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113842.0,
      "end_time": 116554.0,
      "text": "And nearly one out of three are living in a country"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116579.0,
      "end_time": 118595.0,
      "text": "that is facing a water crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119519.0,
      "end_time": 120902.0,
      "text": "I grew up in Jordan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122138.0,
      "end_time": 127439.0,
      "text": "a water-poor country that has experienced absolute water scarcity since 1973."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 128496.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130363.00000000001,
      "text": "And still, in 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 130387.0,
      "end_time": 133442.0,
      "text": "only 10 countries in the world have less water than Jordan."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 134923.0,
      "end_time": 138238.0,
      "text": "So dealing with a lack of water is quite ingrained in my soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138864.0,
      "end_time": 142228.0,
      "text": "As soon as I was old enough to learn how to write my name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 142252.0,
      "end_time": 144714.0,
      "text": "I also learned that I need to conserve water."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 145649.0,
      "end_time": 149659.0,
      "text": "My parents would constantly remind my siblings and I to close the tap"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 149683.0,
      "end_time": 150981.0,
      "text": "when we brushed our teeth."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 151761.0,
      "end_time": 155510.0,
      "text": "We used to fill balloons with flour instead of water when we played."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 156329.0,
      "end_time": 157834.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just as much fun, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 157858.0,
      "end_time": 158941.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 158965.0,
      "end_time": 160132.0,
      "text": "And a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 160156.0,
      "end_time": 163420.0,
      "text": "when my friends and I were dared to do the Ice Bucket Challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 164197.0,
      "end_time": 165768.0,
      "text": "we did that with sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165792.0,
      "end_time": 166942.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 167721.0,
      "end_time": 169981.0,
      "text": "And you might think that, you know, that&#39;s easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 170500.0,
      "end_time": 171246.0,
      "text": "sand is not ice cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 171697.0,
      "end_time": 174315.0,
      "text": "I promise you, sand goes everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174339.0,
      "end_time": 176224.0,
      "text": "and it took ages to get rid of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177970.0,
      "end_time": 179731.0,
      "text": "But what perhaps I didn&#39;t realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179755.0,
      "end_time": 182308.0,
      "text": "as I played with flour balloons as a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182332.0,
      "end_time": 184724.0,
      "text": "and as I poured sand on my head as an adult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185864.0,
      "end_time": 189164.0,
      "text": "is that some of the techniques that seem second nature to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 189188.0,
      "end_time": 191757.0,
      "text": "and to others who live in dry countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191782.0,
      "end_time": 196275.0,
      "text": "might help us all address what is fast becoming a global crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 198272.0,
      "end_time": 200227.0,
      "text": "I wish to share three lessons today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 202297.0,
      "end_time": 204441.0,
      "text": "three lessons from water-poor countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 204465.0,
      "end_time": 209160.0,
      "text": "and how they survived and even thrived despite their water crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210231.0,
      "end_time": 211841.0,
      "text": "Lesson one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211865.0,
      "end_time": 214202.0,
      "text": "tell people how much water they really have."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 215185.0,
      "end_time": 216620.0,
      "text": "In order to solve a problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 216644.0,
      "end_time": 218636.0,
      "text": "we need to acknowledge that we have one."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 219169.0,
      "end_time": 220499.0,
      "text": "And when it comes to water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 220523.0,
      "end_time": 223900.0,
      "text": "people can easily turn a blind eye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 223330.0,
      "end_time": 225873.0,
      "text": "pretending that since water is coming out of the tap now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 225897.0,
      "end_time": 227478.0,
      "text": "everything will be fine forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 228703.0,
      "end_time": 231771.0,
      "text": "But some smart, drought-affected countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 231795.0,
      "end_time": 234179.0,
      "text": "have adopted simple, innovative measures"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234204.0,
      "end_time": 238610.0,
      "text": "to make sure their citizens, their communities and their companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238850.0,
      "end_time": 240710.0,
      "text": "know just how dry their countries are."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 242159.0,
      "end_time": 244576.0,
      "text": "When I was in Cape Town earlier this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 244600.0,
      "end_time": 247500.0,
      "text": "I saw this electronic billboard on the freeway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247524.0,
      "end_time": 249758.0,
      "text": "indicating how much water the city had left."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 251400.0,
      "end_time": 253971.0,
      "text": "This is an idea they may well have borrowed from Australia"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253996.0,
      "end_time": 257643.0,
      "text": "when it faced one of the worst droughts of the country&#39;s history"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 257666.0,
      "end_time": 260321.0,
      "text": "from 1997 to 2009."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 261273.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264783.0,
      "text": "Water levels in Melbourne dropped to a very low capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 264807.0,
      "end_time": 266611.0,
      "text": "of almost 26 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267917.0,
      "end_time": 269655.0,
      "text": "But the city didn&#39;t yell at people."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 270515.0,
      "end_time": 272705.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t plead with them not to use water."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 273427.0,
      "end_time": 277821.0,
      "text": "They used electronic billboards to flash available levels of water"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 277845.0,
      "end_time": 279850.0,
      "text": "to all citizens across the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 280429.0,
      "end_time": 283825.0,
      "text": "They were honestly telling people how much water they really have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283850.0,
      "end_time": 286495.0,
      "text": "and letting them take responsibility for themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 287830.0,
      "end_time": 291900.0,
      "text": "By the end of the drought, this created such a sense of urgency"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 291114.0,
      "end_time": 292760.0,
      "text": "as well as a sense of community."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 293281.0,
      "end_time": 297140.0,
      "text": "Nearly one out of three citizens in Melbourne had invested"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 297380.0,
      "end_time": 300710.0,
      "text": "in installing rainwater holding tanks for their own households."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 301799.0,
      "end_time": 305566.0,
      "text": "Actions that citizens took didn&#39;t stop at installing those tanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 306461.0,
      "end_time": 307789.0,
      "text": "With help from the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 307813.0,
      "end_time": 310205.0,
      "text": "they were able to do something even more impactful."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311509.0,
      "end_time": 312910.0,
      "text": "Taking me to lesson two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 314285.0,
      "end_time": 316702.0,
      "text": "empower people to save water."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 318658.0,
      "end_time": 322135.0,
      "text": "Melbourne wanted people to spend less water in their homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 322636.0,
      "end_time": 325623.0,
      "text": "And one way to do that is to spend less time in the shower."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 326644.0,
      "end_time": 330579.0,
      "text": "However, interviews revealed that some people, women in particular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 330603.0,
      "end_time": 332619.0,
      "text": "weren&#39;t keen on saving water that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 333554.0,
      "end_time": 335250.0,
      "text": "Some of them honestly said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 335274.0,
      "end_time": 337117.0,
      "text": "\"The shower is not just to clean up."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 337141.0,
      "end_time": 338775.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s my sanctuary."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 339218.0,
      "end_time": 342250.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a space I go to relax, not just clean up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 343830.0,
      "end_time": 347130.0,
      "text": "So the city started offering water-efficient showerheads for free."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347638.0,
      "end_time": 351114.0,
      "text": "And then, now some people complained that the showerheads looked ugly"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 351138.0,
      "end_time": 353316.0,
      "text": "or didn&#39;t suit their bathrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 353340.0,
      "end_time": 355748.0,
      "text": "So what I like to call \"The Showerhead Team\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 356423.0,
      "end_time": 358870.0,
      "text": "developed a small water-flow regulator"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358894.0,
      "end_time": 361407.0,
      "text": "that can be fitted into existing showerheads."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 363103.0,
      "end_time": 366446.0,
      "text": "And although showerhead beauty doesn&#39;t matter much to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 366470.0,
      "end_time": 368504.0,
      "text": "I loved how the team didn&#39;t give up"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 368528.0,
      "end_time": 371276.0,
      "text": "and instead came up with a simple, unique solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371300.0,
      "end_time": 373393.0,
      "text": "to empower people to save water."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 374858.0,
      "end_time": 376941.0,
      "text": "Within a span of four years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 376965.0,
      "end_time": 380753.0,
      "text": "more than 460,000 showerheads were replaced."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 381889.0,
      "end_time": 384620.0,
      "text": "When the small regulator was introduced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 384860.0,
      "end_time": 386932.0,
      "text": "more than 100,000 orders of that were done."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 388261.0,
      "end_time": 391457.0,
      "text": "Melbourne succeeded in reducing the water demands per capita"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 391481.0,
      "end_time": 392938.0,
      "text": "by 50 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 393648.0,
      "end_time": 395426.0,
      "text": "In the United Arab Emirates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 395450.0,
      "end_time": 398188.0,
      "text": "the second-most water-scarce country in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 399900.0,
      "end_time": 404348.0,
      "text": "officials designed what they called the \"Business Heroes Toolkit\" in 2010."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407583.0,
      "text": "The aim was to motivate and empower businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 407607.0,
      "end_time": 410115.0,
      "text": "to reduce water and energy consumption."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 411660.0,
      "end_time": 413340.0,
      "text": "The toolkit practically taught companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 413590.0,
      "end_time": 415663.0,
      "text": "how to measure their existing water-consumption levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 416323.0,
      "end_time": 419645.0,
      "text": "and consisted of tips to help them reduce those levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 420517.0,
      "end_time": 421820.0,
      "text": "And it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 421844.0,
      "end_time": 424670.0,
      "text": "Hundreds of organizations downloaded the toolkit."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 425187.0,
      "end_time": 426825.0,
      "text": "And several of them joined"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 426849.0,
      "end_time": 429659.0,
      "text": "what they called the \"Corporate Heroes Network,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 430435.0,
      "end_time": 433352.0,
      "text": "where companies can voluntarily take on a challenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 433376.0,
      "end_time": 436938.0,
      "text": "to reduce their water-consumption levels to preset targets"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 436962.0,
      "end_time": 438599.0,
      "text": "within a period of one year."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 439716.0,
      "end_time": 444536.0,
      "text": "Companies which completed the challenge saved on average 35 percent of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 445409.0,
      "end_time": 447223.0,
      "text": "And one company, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 447247.0,
      "end_time": 451563.0,
      "text": "implemented as many water-saving tips as they could in their office space."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 452178.0,
      "end_time": 457500.0,
      "text": "They replaced their toilet-flushing techniques, taps, showerheads --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 457290.0,
      "end_time": 458218.0,
      "text": "you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 458242.0,
      "end_time": 460709.0,
      "text": "If it saved water, they replaced it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 460733.0,
      "end_time": 464365.0,
      "text": "eventually reducing their employees&#39; water consumption by half."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 465335.0,
      "end_time": 470135.0,
      "text": "Empowering individuals and companies to save water is so critical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 470990.0,
      "end_time": 472482.0,
      "text": "yet not sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 473240.0,
      "end_time": 475720.0,
      "text": "Countries need to look beyond the status quo"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 476264.0,
      "end_time": 479109.0,
      "text": "and implement country-level actions"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 479133.0,
      "end_time": 480395.0,
      "text": "to save water."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 481957.0,
      "end_time": 483893.0,
      "text": "Taking me to lesson three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 483917.0,
      "end_time": 485710.0,
      "text": "look below the surface."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 486268.0,
      "end_time": 489441.0,
      "text": "Water savings can come from unexpected places."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 490555.0,
      "end_time": 493941.0,
      "text": "Singapore is the eighth most water-scarce country in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 494374.0,
      "end_time": 499339.0,
      "text": "It depends on imported water for almost 60 percent of its water needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 500423.0,
      "end_time": 502230.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also a very small island."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 502933.0,
      "end_time": 506609.0,
      "text": "As such, it needs to make use of as much space as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 506633.0,
      "end_time": 507986.0,
      "text": "to catch rainfall."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 509153.0,
      "end_time": 510720.0,
      "text": "So in 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 510744.0,
      "end_time": 512376.0,
      "text": "they built the Marina Barrage."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 512801.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517714.00000000006,
      "text": "It&#39;s the first-ever urban water reservoir built in the middle of the city-state."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 518592.0,
      "end_time": 521885.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the largest water catchment in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 521909.0,
      "end_time": 524680.0,
      "text": "almost one-sixth the size of Singapore."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 524716.0,
      "end_time": 526827.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s so amazing about the Marina Barrage"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 526851.0,
      "end_time": 531766.0,
      "text": "is that it has been built to make the maximum use of its large size"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 531790.0,
      "end_time": 534491.0,
      "text": "and its unexpected yet important location."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 535900.0,
      "end_time": 537506.0,
      "text": "It brings three valuable benefits to the country:"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 538506.0,
      "end_time": 542654.0,
      "text": "it has boosted Singapore&#39;s water supply by 10 percent;"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 543654.0,
      "end_time": 546243.0,
      "text": "it protects low areas around it from floods"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 546267.0,
      "end_time": 548324.0,
      "text": "because of its connection to the sea;"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 549100.0,
      "end_time": 550273.0,
      "text": "and, as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 550297.0,
      "end_time": 552887.0,
      "text": "it acts as a beautiful lifestyle attraction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 552911.0,
      "end_time": 554758.0,
      "text": "hosting several events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 554783.0,
      "end_time": 557595.0,
      "text": "from art exhibitions to music festivals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 557619.0,
      "end_time": 561765.0,
      "text": "attracting joggers, bikers, tourists all around that area."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 563521.0,
      "end_time": 565848.0,
      "text": "Now, not all initiatives need to be stunning"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 565872.0,
      "end_time": 567210.0,
      "text": "or even visible."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 567923.0,
      "end_time": 571816.0,
      "text": "My first home, Jordan, realized that agriculture is consuming"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 571840.0,
      "end_time": 574363.0,
      "text": "the majority of its fresh water."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 575396.0,
      "end_time": 577636.0,
      "text": "They really wanted to encourage farmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 577660.0,
      "end_time": 580886.0,
      "text": "to focus on growing low water-intensive crops."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582136.0,
      "end_time": 583334.0,
      "text": "To achieve that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 583359.0,
      "end_time": 588258.0,
      "text": "the local agriculture is increasing its focus on date palms and grapevines."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 589770.0,
      "end_time": 592577.0,
      "text": "Those two are much more tolerant to drought conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 592601.0,
      "end_time": 594452.0,
      "text": "than many other fruits and vegetables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 594941.0,
      "end_time": 596528.0,
      "text": "and at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 596552.0,
      "end_time": 601719.0,
      "text": "they are considered high-value crops, both locally and internationally."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 602711.0,
      "end_time": 604271.0,
      "text": "Locals in Namibia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 605730.0,
      "end_time": 608561.0,
      "text": "one of the most arid countries in Southern Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 608585.0,
      "end_time": 612984.0,
      "text": "have been drinking recycled water since 1968."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 613334.0,
      "end_time": 616200.0,
      "text": "Now, you may tell me many countries recycle water."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 616767.0,
      "end_time": 618960.0,
      "text": "I would say yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 618569.0,
      "end_time": 620789.0,
      "text": "But very few use it for drinking purposes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 621738.0,
      "end_time": 624189.0,
      "text": "mostly because people don&#39;t like the thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 624213.0,
      "end_time": 627709.0,
      "text": "of water that was in their toilets going to their taps."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 628295.0,
      "end_time": 630834.0,
      "text": "But Namibia could not afford to think that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 631528.0,
      "end_time": 634374.0,
      "text": "They looked below the surface to save water."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 635428.0,
      "end_time": 637189.0,
      "text": "They are now a great example"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 637214.0,
      "end_time": 641869.0,
      "text": "of how, when countries purify waste water to drinking standards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 641893.0,
      "end_time": 644910.0,
      "text": "they can ease their water shortages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 644672.0,
      "end_time": 646185.0,
      "text": "and in Namibia&#39;s case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 646209.0,
      "end_time": 651402.0,
      "text": "provide drinking water for more than 300,000 citizens in its capital city."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 652714.0,
      "end_time": 656850.0,
      "text": "As more countries which used to be more water rich"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 656874.0,
      "end_time": 658714.0,
      "text": "are becoming water scarce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 659703.0,
      "end_time": 662384.0,
      "text": "I say we don&#39;t need to reinvent the wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 663586.0,
      "end_time": 666839.0,
      "text": "If we just look at what water-poor countries have done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 667561.0,
      "end_time": 669353.0,
      "text": "the solutions are out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 670300.0,
      "end_time": 673261.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s really just up to all of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 673285.0,
      "end_time": 674637.0,
      "text": "to take action."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 675495.0,
      "end_time": 676677.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 676701.0,
      "end_time": 679317.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}